title: Changed my name
body:
I changed my name but it did not change on the website.
Is there something i have to do? I am confused about
this.

replies.body:
It looks like your Summoner and Boards profiles had fallen out of sync, but are now synced and everything looks good!

Let me know if you have any questions. ^.^

Ya @-@ i can not go onto my profile.
Can i has help
Note: i can not go to my profile from the top right drown down menu

Can you try using a different web browser or clear your browser data using [this guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)?

If anything changes, let me know.
All you have to do is log out, for future people having this problem
